articles.title: Álex Palou wins Indianapolis 500, Kyle Larson’s quest for the ‘Double’ comes to an end after wreck - CNN
articles.description: “The Greatest Spectacle in Racing” certainly lived up to its name after Álex Palou took the checkered flag to win the 109th running of the Indianapolis 500 on Sunday.
